+```bash
+microk8s config > ~/.kube/config
+export KUBECONFIG=~/.kube/config
+```
+
+To make the `KUBECONFIG` environment variable persistent, add the `export` command to your shell's configuration file (e.g., `~/.bashrc` or `~/.zshrc`).
